$PAR
Compute \( \cosh (x)  \) and \( $trig \), assuming \( \sinh (x) = $sinhx \).  
$PAR

\( \cosh (x) = \) \{ans_rule() \} $BR
\( $trig = \) \{ans_rule() \}

