SOLUTION(EV3(<<'END_SOLUTION'));
$PAR
$SOL
$BR
Using the identity \( \cosh^2x-\sinh^2x=1 \), it follows that \( \cosh^2x-($sinhx)^2=1 \), so that 
\[ \cosh x= $coshx .  \]
Then, by definition, 
\[ $trig = $trigtex = $trigx \]
$BR

